{
  "texts": [
    "Many catalogues incorporate all three technologies (30%), i.e.",
    "REST API, web search GUI, and SPARQL endpoint, especially the catalogues based on the OntoPortal software 22.",
    "These catalogues provide data with no authentications/restrictions, and contents are freely available without restrictions.",
    "In addition, for most of them, external/registered users can add/propose new semantic artefacts to be included.",
